statements.sql: select count(*) as aggregate from `ofoods` inner join `ads` on `ads`.`id` = `ofoods`.`ads_id` inner join `media` on `media`.`model_id` = `ads`.`id` and media.id = (SELECT MIN(id) FROM media WHERE media.model_id = ads.id) inner join `users` on `users`.`id` = `ads`.`user_id` inner join `kategori_food` on `kategori_food`.`oFood_id` = `ofoods`.`id` inner join `sup_kategoris` on `sup_kategoris`.`id` = `kategori_food`.`kategori_id` inner join `kategoris` on `kategoris`.`id` = `sup_kategoris`.`kategori_id` where `kategoris`.`nama` = 'Fruits' and `ads`.`is_active` = 1 and (`ads`.`title` like '%%' or `users`.`name` like '%%' or `ads`.`status` like '%%' or `ads`.`is_active` like '%%')

select CONCAT('http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/', media.id, '/', media.file_name) AS image_path, `ads`.`title`, `users`.`name` as `name_user`, `ads`.`status`, `ads`.`is_active`, `ads`.`id` as `ads_id`, `media`.`id` as `media_id`, `media`.`file_name` as `file_name`, `ofoods`.*, `ads`.`slug`,
(6371 * acos(
cos(radians(-6.1833216))
* cos(radians(ofoods.districtLocation_lat))
* cos(radians(ofoods.districtLocation_long) - radians(106.6041344))
+ sin(radians(-6.1833216))
* sin(radians(ofoods.districtLocation_lat))
)) AS distance
from `ofoods` inner join `ads` on `ads`.`id` = `ofoods`.`ads_id` inner join `media` on `media`.`model_id` = `ads`.`id` and media.id = (SELECT MIN(id) FROM media WHERE media.model_id = ads.id) inner join `users` on `users`.`id` = `ads`.`user_id` inner join `kategori_food` on `kategori_food`.`oFood_id` = `ofoods`.`id` inner join `sup_kategoris` on `sup_kategoris`.`id` = `kategori_food`.`kategori_id` inner join `kategoris` on `kategoris`.`id` = `sup_kategoris`.`kategori_id` where `kategoris`.`nama` = 'Fruits' and `ads`.`is_active` = 1 and (`ads`.`title` like '%%' or `users`.`name` like '%%' or `ads`.`status` like '%%' or `ads`.`is_active` like '%%') order by `ads`.`id` desc limit 10 offset 0
